# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Dhyana Stays — Root Environment Template
# This file is a pointer. Each app has its own .env.example:
#
#   apps/api/.env.example          ← Backend (NestJS) — all API variables
#   apps/web/.env.local.example    ← Frontend (Next.js) — NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables
#
# See docs/auth0-setup.md for Auth0 configuration instructions.
# See docs/runbook.md for local development setup.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
